{"tid":1699072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[草木皆兵]如果香港人每日都帶裝備返工返學行街食飯，有突發示威就參與，無就回家，警察可以點防？","createTime":"2019-11-08T02:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T03:13:38.000Z","uid":103513,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f80ed0c3c61106b47b5afb589176a31c824a6c","tid":1699072,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"黑警日日都MON POST，睇準市民每次行動都需要事前文宣呼籲、準備物資先出動，變相佢地都可以做足準備、計劃好晒點樣趕示威者、點樣鳩拉、點樣自編自導陷害<br />\n<br />\n咁如果香港人日日都帶裝備出街，有野發生就加入，無就正常返工放工，警察係咪要即刻戒嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係周街抽查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果日日都周圍抽查市民，咁一定會日日都捉錯良民，日日都擾民畀街坊屌，長遠仲會令社會出現恐慌，搞到啲人唔敢行街&hellip;&hellip;咁聖誕新年咪&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申我話『如果』，唔係鼓勵人咁做，純粹推演緊有人可能會咁做，善意提醒嚟架黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dc0354948f753b9b2c41b6884bf71a40c96656","tid":1699072,"uid":103513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"到時文宣組突然搞場快閃式示威，一聲令下一呼百應，黑警MON POST都MON唔切，香港治安一定會好亂，商家表示怕怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53064171524020eb8d8e3a942bf5ecc793868b5","tid":1699072,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"會stop and search"},{"pid":"2a96a854fd1b19b1fd54875b956d6d5fc86273f3","tid":1699072,"uid":103513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f53064171524020eb8d8e3a942bf5ecc793868b5","tid":1699072,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"會stop and search"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"日日都咁做？<br />\n返工放工時段？<br />\n好擾民喎<br />\n況且如果當日無示威活動，咁係咪背囊有口罩有頭盔都犯法？"},{"pid":"4e70d20396c6c